Changelog:

Mi 8:
- Upstream to 4.9.163
- Switched to aosp clang 9.0.1
- Fixed system freezing and stuttering
- Remove simple MSM thermal and simple low memory killer
- Switched to userspace lmk
- Dynamic stune boost optimised
- Removed API for marking k-threads as performance critical
- Disable SECCOMP 
- Update boosting drivers
- Tick rate back to 300hz
- Removed bfq
- cfq is default i/o scheduler 
- Readahead set to 128kb 
- Optimisation for arm64
- Lots of other fixes and optimisations

Rom:
- Revert to QuickStep launcher
- Expanded volume panel
- Improved statusbar icon padding
- Lockscreen D2TS works on whole screen
- WiFi: Reimplemented WPS
- Fixed manual network selection
- Fixed display of mobile network icons
- Fixed system ui crash when pinning screen
- Some themes fixes
- Various fixes and improvements
- Update translations
